---
title: Smart Cheddar Pork Patties with Maple-BBQ Sauce and Fresh Salad
description: These summer flavours with a kiss of sweetness will leave your tastebuds begging for more. Savoury pork patties are basted in a maple-BBQ sauce and topped with sharp cheddar. A fresh apple and cranberry salad make this meal both delicious and nutritious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/galettes-de-porc-au-cheddar-d665f06f.jpg
